1.text: Do you have time to look around you when you are free? If so, read and guess.
1.ssml: <speak><prosody rate='slow'>Do you have time to look around you when you are free? If so, read and guess.</prosody></speak>

2.text: I am the star at the centre of your solar system. Your planet Earth revolves around me. I give you light, heat and energy. I help plants to grow. I also help plants to produce food. I am your friend.
2.ssml: <speak><prosody rate='slow'>I am the star at the centre of your solar system. Your planet Earth revolves around me. I give you light, heat and energy. I help plants to grow. I also help plants to produce food. I am your friend.</prosody></speak>

3.text: I am all around you. I contain Oxygen. All living things need Oxygen to breathe. I also help plants to produce food. When I move fast, you call me the wind.
3.ssml: <speak><prosody rate='slow'>I am all around you. I contain Oxygen. All living things need Oxygen to breathe. I also help plants to produce food. When I move fast, you call me the wind.</prosody></speak>

4.text: I come down to the Earth as rain and fill wells, rivers and oceans. I quench your thirst. You need me for cooking, bathing and washing. I also help plants to grow.
4.ssml: <speak><prosody rate='slow'>I come down to the Earth as rain and fill wells, rivers and oceans. I quench your thirst. You need me for cooking, bathing and washing. I also help plants to grow.</prosody></speak>

5.text: We give you Oxygen to breathe. We produce food for you. We give you shade. You make clothes, medicine, timber and many other things using us. We also make your world beautiful.
5.ssml: <speak><prosody rate='slow'>We give you Oxygen to breathe. We produce food for you. We give you shade. You make clothes, medicine, timber and many other things using us. We also make your world beautiful.</prosody></speak>

6.text: I am your home. I am the only planet in our solar system with life and liquid water. People, animals and plants are my children. I have mountains, valleys, forests, rivers, deserts and many other places for all of you.
